		<title>11 Creative Strategies for Facebook Ad Targeting After the Changes</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2019/04/29/facebook-ad-targeting-strategies</link>
					<comments>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2019/04/29/facebook-ad-targeting-strategies#respond</comments>
		
