					<description><![CDATA[<p>The only thing better than leads is free leads! Learn how to pin a lead ad on Facebook so you can drive free leads from your business page. It's simple, easy, and yes--truly free!</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2018/07/24/facebook-free-leads">Top Secret: How to Get Free Leads from Facebook</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
